		<category><![CDATA[Ayn Hilwa]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.jihadica.com/?p=218</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[
Over the weekend, Shihada Jawhar was killed in the Ayn Hilwa refugee camp in Lebanon, along with two others, in fighting between Jund al-Sham, a Sunni militant group, and Fatah.
Jawhar, who fought for al-Qaeda in Iraq, is best known for a revealing interview with al-`Arabiyya&#8217;s program &#8220;Death Industry&#8221; upon his return to Ayn Hilwa.   As [...]<script type="text/javascript">SHARETHIS.addEntry({ title: "Jihadi Action Hero Dies in Ayn Hilwa, Lebanon", url: "http://www.jihadica.com/jihadi-action-hero-dies-in-ayn-hilwa-lebanon/" });</script>]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.jihadica.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/shihada-jawhar-dead.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-219" title="shihada-jawhar-dead" src="http://www.jihadica.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/shihada-jawhar-dead-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a></p>
<p>Over the weekend, Shihada Jawhar was killed in the Ayn Hilwa refugee camp in Lebanon, along with two others, in <a href="http://www.reuters.com/article/latestCrisis/idUSL20606651" onclick="urchinTracker('/outgoing/www.reuters.com/article/latestCrisis/idUSL20606651?referer=');">fighting</a> between Jund al-Sham, a Sunni militant group, and Fatah.</p>
<p>Jawhar, who fought for al-Qaeda in Iraq, is best known for a revealing <a href="http://www.memritv.org/clip/en/1624.htm" onclick="urchinTracker('/outgoing/www.memritv.org/clip/en/1624.htm?referer=');">interview</a> with al-`Arabiyya&#8217;s program &#8220;Death Industry&#8221; upon his return to Ayn Hilwa.   As you can see from his exchange with the host, Shihada typifies the Jihadi action hero <a href="http://www.jihadica.com/proof-that-sincere-sunnis-are-fighting-in-tripoli-lebanon/">I wrote about</a> a few days ago.  He&#8217;s a little less cocky in later a New York Times <a href="http://video.on.nytimes.com/?fr_story=a2aa2da96e324b5c6a30da24ea819454dde408e4" onclick="urchinTracker('/outgoing/video.on.nytimes.com/?fr_story=a2aa2da96e324b5c6a30da24ea819454dde408e4&referer=');">interview</a>, probably because he had just burned himself making a bomb.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.jihadica.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/shihada-jawhar-with-friends.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-220" title="shihada-jawhar-with-friends" src="http://www.jihadica.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/shihada-jawhar-with-friends-300x182.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="182" /></a></p>
<p>Reaction on the forums is mixed.  Some feel that Shihada was just a loudmouth who got what was coming to him, while others view him as a hero.</p>
<p><a href="http://sharethis.com/item?&wp=2.5.1&amp;publisher=adab62c7-0bc6-488f-832a-aab9e4abcf47&amp;title=Jihadi+Action+Hero+Dies+in+Ayn+Hilwa%2C+Lebanon&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jihadica.com%2Fjihadi-action-hero-dies-in-ayn-hilwa-lebanon%2F" onclick="urchinTracker('/outgoing/sharethis.com/item?_wp=2.5.1_amp_publisher=adab62c7-0bc6-488f-832a-aab9e4abcf47_amp_title=Jihadi+Action+Hero+Dies+in+Ayn+Hilwa_2C+Lebanon_amp_url=http_3A_2F_2Fwww.jihadica.com_2Fjihadi-action-hero-dies-in-ayn-hilwa-lebanon_2F&referer=');">ShareThis</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
