		<title>25 Kuwaitis Fighting for al-Qaeda in Diyala Province</title>
		<link>http://www.jihadica.com/25-kuwaitis-fighting-for-al-qaeda-in-diyala-province/</link>
		<comments>http://www.jihadica.com/25-kuwaitis-fighting-for-al-qaeda-in-diyala-province/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 16 Jul 2008 22:33:50 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Will</dc:creator>
		
		<category><![CDATA[AQ in Iraq]]></category>

